{"tid":1351524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對恐懼 我地應該","createTime":"2019-07-22T15:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T00:31:57.000Z","uid":258010,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"67273cfcbcfb6c319731436cb3b4030714fffe0d","tid":1351524,"uid":258010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"From Simon Lui (Facebook)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156060495911105%26set%3Da.45435071104%26type%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2wsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=17071eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156060495911105&amp;set=a.45435071104&amp;type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我經歷過波士頓馬拉松爆炸案，明白襲擊後的恐怖<br />\n1) 爆炸前30分鐘，我仍在Boylston st現場，只是早走了<br />\n2) MIT校警就在我Lab樓下(Building 32)被槍殺，只是我偷懶無返工(偷懶萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n我嗰晚好驚，本來諗住「一星期唔出街，以後見人都要提防」... 但原來我錯了<br />\n<br />\n【恐佈分子的目的，不是要讓100人死掉，而是要令幾億人害怕】<br />\n<br />\n是波士頓人教曉我，面對恐懼就要更勇敢。因為爆炸後第二晚，波士頓人竟然這樣：<br />\n- 不躲在家中，照常出街跑步<br />\n- 不讓恐懼擴散，反而故意外出食飯購物<br />\n- 人與人之間的信任沒有動搖。反而整網頁讓居民登記，開放自己家，讓因爆炸案錯過火車的旅人住一晚 <br />\n<br />\n「開放自己家！黐線㗎！引狼入室！」不是的<br />\n- 若恐佈分子要襲擊，點會無方法？<br />\n- 由華盛頓來旅行但錯過火車嘅自己人，點會睇唔出？幫佢點會有事？<br />\n- 自己人互相幫助，其實安全得很<br />\n- 所以最後，我自己都踩單車出去飲咖啡，重買水比站崗嘅人<br />\n<br />\n恐佈分子的失敗，在於居民鎮定不害怕，在於鄰里關係沒有動搖。若要防範恐佈分子，不是要人人自危，而是要把問題源頭清掉吧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，守望相助，不要落單，齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9363db32904a06c014872e02211e362cac34edab","tid":1351524,"uid":73875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"唔好輸比黑勢力睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22d5009d73dc1a9ad1ca40b32a0c378c312b557","tid":1351524,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"睇下今日屯元天，以後會由黑社會管香港，黑警暗地提供資源"},{"pid":"57241b2452b92c46f57a71c9ed23c3770bbcf684","tid":1351524,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:45:25.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"5c4479257d2cde9f7e4271190e7e6fba59083e29","tid":1351524,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8ad9085da39c261fd559a4aa0594d3ffc5eae59b","tid":1351524,"uid":258010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"唔好屈服同時都要be water<br />\n唔好做人沙包<br />\n我地一路以來對狗嘅經驗話俾我地知<br />\n最頂癮嘅做法<br />\n就係佢地要行動前<br />\n我地散哂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">得佢谷住谷住射唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"39aa461f02d45dc7de2d3f0b7d1031fb14821b82","tid":1351524,"uid":258010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad9085da39c261fd559a4aa0594d3ffc5eae59b","tid":1351524,"uid":258010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"唔好屈服同時都要be water<br />\n唔好做人沙包<br />\n我地一路以來對狗嘅經驗話俾我地知<br />\n最頂癮嘅做法<br />\n就係佢地要行動前<br />\n我地散哂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">得佢谷住谷住射唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"對住呢班鄉黑 人海戰術<br />\n佢地吹雞我地就散<br />\n唔對路嘅時候保命先<br />\n日常嘅時候<br />\n我地要比以往<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">活得最精彩</span></span>"},{"pid":"465eb3ef2c5605b14dbac71b9e70e6701c3cba15","tid":1351524,"uid":212288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港！ 時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n有少少野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350871</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3badd1b09933db4461506c94ee09306a3ea2fcc6","tid":1351524,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"拒絕活在恐懼之中<br />\n😱😱😱😱😱😱😱😱"},{"pid":"732ca32f7cd4e1f6dfd8b9b9b393ae2ec22a5bd3","tid":1351524,"uid":276548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"有班撚樣 有支那怕事DNA 不停吹幫鄉黑 攪到佢地自大晒<br />\n先有元朗亂打人既事 面對佢地唔可以退"},{"pid":"fdd4df2658e7b18a66ea4b39d651303041e0074b","tid":1351524,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"推！一齊互助！<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我冇野講 我有權唔解鎖\n我要搵律師 (背定律師電話)\n我唔簽任何文件 我要警誡記錄\n我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所\n我唔舒服要去醫院\n我要睇你委任證同編號</code></pre>"},{"pid":"573bda43e30eb35e7528bdaf2a795796970c797e","tid":1351524,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 小弟嘅白宮聯署差四分一人咋<br />\n希望request國際人道救援/援助 人權監察<br />\n已經有七萬四千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住confirm email<br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867e75d328315f4d7209aa5ff30367394805f2fd","tid":1351524,"uid":276625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46228d3744594894fbdc9bd268301d32fc5cf305","tid":1351524,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB